data.name: Calendar
desc: A calendar as returned in a sequence by XLocaleData.getAllCalendars().

items.name: Default
lines: if this is the default calendar for a given locale.

items.name: MinimumNumberOfDaysForFirstWeek
lines: how many days must reside in the first week of a year.

items.name: Name
lines: the name of the calendar, for example, Gregorian.

items.name: StartOfWeek
lines: the ID of the day with which the week begins.

items.name: Days
lines: the days of the week, see also CalendarItem.

items.name: Eras
lines: the possible eras, see also CalendarItem.

items.name: Months
lines: the months of the year, see also CalendarItem.
